ActAeronautics Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canadian Aviation Regulations (Manuals)
PrecisRegulations amending the CANADIAN AVIATION REGULATIONS (MANUALS) in order to (1) harmonize certain requirements in the Regulations pertaining to manuals with the enabling authorities under the AERAUTICS ACT; and (2) eliminate any unnecessary duplication of text.
